{"tid":902132,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"白蘭樹下香港Gin氈酒，點睇？","createTime":"2018-11-14T14:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T18:15:06.000Z","uid":154054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"44807f2d8ca4364dc73d82f136bc98f925779cb7","tid":902132,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:44:52.000Z","msg":"「 白蘭花，好香好靚，十蚊三紮!」 盛夏街頭，一個阿婆，一片蕉葉，地攤賣花。 花瓣素白，花托雅綠，淡麗幽芳，消暑清涼， 你我經過，幫吓婆婆，做個好心，手留餘香，尋常不過。 然而，看在英國回流的調酒師阿 Kit眼裡，盞盞夏令白花， 既是吾土吾情，集體回憶，更是造氈酒入釀，意想不到的好材料⋯⋯今年，他就成功用大埔林村的白蘭花，蒸餾出「白蘭樹下」(Perfume Trees)，一瓶屬於香港的Gin。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Mh1_0Wg1f0_GD4sF.Mfljw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/__831/94c22c3b862f99f61568cfde93bec469\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FMh1_0Wg1f0_GD4sF.Mfljw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2F__831%2F94c22c3b862f99f61568cfde93bec469&h=1d4b68fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://hktravelnow.yahoo.com/%E7%99%BD%E8%98%AD%E6%A8%B9%E4%B8%8B-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AFgin%E6%B0%88%E9%85%92-%E7%99%BD%E8%98%AD%E8%8A%B1-%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%9F%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E9%87%80%E8%A3%BD-%E5%81%9Acocktail-100753807.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhktravelnow.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2599%25BD%25E8%2598%25AD%25E6%25A8%25B9%25E4%25B8%258B-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AFgin%25E6%25B0%2588%25E9%2585%2592-%25E7%2599%25BD%25E8%2598%25AD%25E8%258A%25B1-%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%259F%25E6%259D%2590%25E6%2596%2599%25E9%2587%2580%25E8%25A3%25BD-%25E5%2581%259Acocktail-100753807.html&d=i8WUAnXc8SZEx4Gy6C0J8DOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=06a962ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hktravelnow.yahoo.com/%E7%99%BD%E8%98%AD%E6%A8%B9%E4%B8%8B-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AFgin%E6%B0%88%E9%85%92-%E7%99%BD%E8%98%AD%E8%8A%B1-%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%9F%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E9%87%80%E8%A3%BD-%E5%81%9Acocktail